Package: libsertial-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: SeRTial - zero-allocation C++20 binary serialization (dev headers)
 High-performance, stack-only serialization library using compile-time
 struct reflection via reflect-cpp. Provides fixed_vector, fixed_string,
 RingBuffer containers with compile-time size computation.

Package: sertial-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: SeRTial - schema inspection CLI tool
 The sertial-inspect command-line tool for visualising SeRTial message
 layouts at runtime.
